Description: Small fragment from the belly of a pottery closed vessel; hard, porous, red clay, Munsell 10YR 5/4 (weak red).
Bibliographic references: Weber 2012 / Untersuchungen zur archaischen griechischen Keramik aus anderen ägyptischen Fundorten (TD 338)
Acquisition notes: Found unregistered in the Department in 2010, in a box with other sherds from Tell Dafana.
